Our little miracle🥹💛

A secret we have been keeping for what feels like YEARS now is finally out!!!!! Our story is nothing short of miraculous, and we are SO excited to finally share it with you all!!!☺️☺️☺️

When we first found out and I told my parents, they drove all the way here and took us out to dinner. At the dinner, my mom said, “If you want to make God laugh, tell him about your plans.” (Both of our families have been so unbelievably supportive, and I’m not sure I would have survived these past months without my MOM🥹🥹🥹)

THAT ONE HIT HOME PHEWWWW! I am the biggest planner EVER, and in my book, Joey and I would get married next June and start trying for kids in 2-3 years. The night we found out….we were in complete disbelief and to be honest, NOT READY AT ALL. We did not feel like we were prepared to be parents!!!!! But then again, who really is?? It’s the greatest blessing no matter when it happens. 

Do you all remember when I posted about my grandpa passing? We found out I was pregnant a week before that happened…to say the emotions were ALL OVER THE PLACE for a couple of weeks is an understatement. The best part is that my grandma was able to tell him I was pregnant before he passed, and he had the biggest smile on his face ever 😭😭😭😭

We all know now that God was blessing us with another member in the family while he was welcoming another one home🧡

I look at Joey now and think back to when we met at a house party back in 2016, and all I can think is how I met my soulmate back then and how incredible it is that God now wants us to begin a family together. 🥹 

So here’s to expanding the BACHIE family (yes, we also got married yesterday HAHAHA still doing our big Catholic wedding + reception next year though!!!) with a child that is already adored, loved, and cared for by so many people!!!!☺️🫶🏻 CAN’T WAIT TO SQUEEZE YOU LIL BEEB! 🥰🥰🥰🥰

OH and you bet your bottom dollar all of you and my clients are coming along for the PREGNANT PHASE OF BBH BABY🏋🏼‍♀️🤪 Honestly beyond STOKED to add this whole NEW side to my business!!! 🫶🏻

P.S. stay tuned for a sit down vlog where I REALLY get into all the details of these past few months🤪🤪🤪
